info:
  description:  |
    Adapted from CIM data models. Modified IEEE DC2A direct current commutator exciters with speed input, one more leg block in feedback loop and without underexcitation limiters (UEL) inputs.  DC type 2 excitation system model with added speed multiplier, added lead-lag, and voltage-dependent limits.
  title: ExcDC2A
  version: "1.0.0"
openapi: "3.0.0"

  /ngsi-ld/v1/entities: 
    get: 
      description: "Retrieve a set of entities which matches a specific query from an NGSI-LD system"
      parameters: 
        - 
          in: query
          name: type
          required: true
          schema: 
            enum: 
              - ExcDC2A
            type: string
      responses: 
        ? "200"
        : 
          content: 
            application/ld+json: 
              examples: 
                keyvalues: 
                  summary: "Key-Values Pairs"
                  value: 
                    - 
                      $ref: "https://smart-data-models.github.io/dataModel.EnergyCIM/ExcDC2A/examples/example.json"
                normalized:

                  value: 
                    - 
                      $ref: "https://smart-data-models.github.io/dataModel.EnergyCIM/ExcDC2A/examples/example-normalized.jsonld"
          description: OK
      tags: 
        - ngsi-ld

    description: "NGSI-LD Linked-data Format"
    name: ngsi-ld
